snippet.textDisplay: How can so many people listening to songs here can even notice the religion of the singer!!! No one noticed when Rafi or Yesudas or Kishore sang. People are making sure that they know the religion of the singer, as if it matters!!! And the commentators  pretend to be peace-lovers by praising the singers' guts or heart to sing another religion's songs. In the India I know of, no one cared about all these. Naushad or Madan Mohan or Mehdi Hassan or Ilayaraja or Bhupen Hazarika or Abida Parveen are not Muslim or Hindu musicians. Remember, it was the religions that caused the endless pain that was partition. The hate in your minds was created by religions. No need to pat each others back, after asking for respective religion or caste. Don't ask. Don't notice. Destroy the strangler-fig hold of religions in our minds. Be free.
